	<h4 class="process-title blue">What is the relevance of writing a Thesis?</h4>
	<p class="main-article">Although the long and arduous task in thesis writing can discourage the writer in pursuing the project, thesis writing can be a satisfying experience as it gives writers the chance to exercise their academic and professional freedom. Thesis writing, although considered by many as merely an academic requirement, is relevant in the sense that it provides opportunities both for personal and professional advancement.</p>
	<h4 class="process-title">1. Personal Advancement</h4>
	<ul class="list-blue-bullets">
		<li><strong>thesis writing develops creativity</strong>
			<p>Thesis writing develops creativity in a way that it enhances the researcher’s ability to find other ways in interpreting ideas, things, events, and people. In the process of finding ways to settle a problem, people will be able to integrate their skills as well as bring together different ideas to arrive at a logical and practical solution. In thesis writing, writers are given the opportunity to explore ideas and provide their own insights on such ideas. As these ideas are product of intelligent research, creativity, and critical thinking, those contribute to advancement in specific fields of research.</p>
		</li>
		<li><strong>develops critical thinking skills</strong>
			<p>Thesis writing develops the critical thinking skills of researchers as they strive to understand, analyze, and interpret the information they have gathered from their research. When critical thinking skills are developed, people will be able to find productive and practical solutions to their problems. In addition, they will be able to evaluate situations analytically, which enable them to pass judgments objectively.</p>
		</li>
		<li><strong>career advancement</strong>
			<p>Thesis projects can be good sources of innovations in science, politics, and art. Should research projects make relevant contributions to the society; the credits will go to the researcher. Researchers, in turn, will benefit from their credits as they would have the chance to improve their career and find higher-paying jobs. Highly recognized thesis writers even received research grants, scholarships, and awards.</p>
		</li>
	</ul>
	<h4 class="process-title">2. Professional Advancement</h4>
	<ul class="list-blue-bullets">
		<li><strong>develops professional maturity and academic success</strong>
			<p>In the academic context, thesis writing is a productive and rewarding experience as it allows students to demonstrate their level of understanding and professionalism. As thesis writing is one of the requirements in pursuing a graduate or post-graduate degree, accomplishing a thesis project is an achievement as it means passing the course. In colleges and universities, there are even awards given to students who passed the best thesis. Thus, the quality of the thesis project is one of the factors that determine one’s performance as a student.</p>
		</li>
		<li><strong>contributes to advances in specific fields</strong>
			<p>Thesis projects are also one of the sources of advancement in science, art, and other fields of study; it contains major breakthroughs, which include new policy levels, theories, and concepts. These breakthroughs contribute to the improvement of human civilization as those are integrated in business policies and government system. Furthermore, thesis projects are good starting points in conducting  in-depth studies. Thesis projects provide ideas concerning previously studied materials. Accordingly, later thesis projects may base on earlier studies and advance those to a new level of investigation.</p>
		</li>
	</ul>
